SQL_STMT_U.val: select order_header.order_id, order_header.billing_contact_id, Components.component_title,content_component.content, components.component_id, order_lines.product_id, order_header.Created_Date, order_header.shipping_address_code, order_header.description from Components, order_header, order_lines, product, content_component where Components.component_id = order_lines.component_id and order_lines.order_id = order_header.order_id and order_header.order_status_cd = 11 and order_lines.product_id = product.product_id and product.product_type_cd = 11 and components.component_id = content_component.component_id
